      <title>乌克兰总统签署法律降低战时征兵年龄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ukrainian-president-signs-law-to-reduce-wartime-conscription-age</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽伦斯基最初拒绝了一项降低战争期间征兵年龄的法案，该法案于大约一年前被议会通过。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ukrainian-president-signs-law-to-reduce-wartime-conscription-age</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着紧张局势加剧，拜登在斋月期间会见穆斯林领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-meets-with-muslim-leaders-during-ramadan-as-tensions-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在白宫处理以色列与哈马斯战争的方式受到越来越多的批评之际，总统乔·拜登将与一群穆斯林工作人员会面，纪念斋月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-meets-with-muslim-leaders-during-ramadan-as-tensions-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:58:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登、习近平通电话谈论人工智能风险、俄罗斯和芬太尼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-xi-spoke-by-phone-to-manage-world-tensions-opportunities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登和中国国家主席习近平周二通电话，这是自去年 11 月在加州会晤以来他们的首次一对一沟通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-xi-spoke-by-phone-to-manage-world-tensions-opportunities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国就加沙援助人员死亡事件召见以色列大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/uk-summons-israeli-ambassador-over-gaza-aid-worker-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交部表示，世界中央厨房的七名援助人员在加沙遇害后，英国外交部召见了以色列大使，外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦称这些死亡事件“完全不可接受”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/uk-summons-israeli-ambassador-over-gaza-aid-worker-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约提议设立1000亿美元五年基金援助乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nato-proposes-100-billion-five-year-fund-to-support-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格提议在五年内为乌克兰建立一个价值 1000 亿美元的盟国捐款基金，作为联盟领导人 7 月齐聚华盛顿时签署的一揽子计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nato-proposes-100-billion-five-year-fund-to-support-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:10:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑海输给乌克兰后俄罗斯重组海军指挥部</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/russia-shakes-up-navy-command-after-black-sea-losses-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在黑海舰队的一系列舰艇在乌克兰的袭击中损失后，俄罗斯国防部宣布对海军最高职位进行改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/russia-shakes-up-navy-command-after-black-sea-losses-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:15:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗誓言惩罚以色列袭击驻叙利亚大使馆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗在指责以色列对其驻叙利亚大使馆发动致命空袭后发誓要对以色列进行报复——这是双方因加沙战争而不断升级的冲突中罕见的直接对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/iran-says-sent-us-message-over-deadly-israeli-strike-on-compound</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 06:11:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官在封口费审判前扩大了特朗普的禁言令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/trump-gag-order-expanded-by-ny-judge-before-hush-money-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在前总统在社交媒体上攻击法官和他的女儿后，主持唐纳德·特朗普封口费审判的纽约法官扩大了该案的禁言令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/trump-gag-order-expanded-by-ny-judge-before-hush-money-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:17:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最终医疗保险优惠率令人失望，健康保险公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国监管机构没有像业界预期的那样增加私人医疗保险计划的支付，健康保险股周二暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——美国历史上没有其他候选人面临过这样的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
